Radix sort 

Lesson learned
-- When accumulating the index in counting sort, make sure to save previous non-zero value and add on top of that.  Basically only looking at positive values. 
-- The counting array index are tricky, be careful. 
-- Write output array to output array, then deep copy output array back to original array. Simply a=b wonâ€™t work. 
